lore:
A spiked collar with a garish golden hue, the signature accessory of Kirke. The celestial dog followed his instincts and became the self-appointed guardian of mankind's new generation, assuming a form most befitting the spirit of their time.

Even in human form, Kirke has a distinctive doglike demeanor about him, though one of good breeding and obedience. He speaks little, preferring actions over words, but will always offer an encouraging nudge when it's most needed.

Though some believe this collar to be only for show, those who have crossed Kirke's charges tend to say otherwise...
name: Carlancas
